14th.]—In the morning I reviewed the whole eighth book of the Iliad;
went through the Racines Grecques, 48—52, and finished the Enquiry,
p. 216—335.

4th.]—I read second Memoire sur la Danse, tom. i. Mem. p. 117—136;
Memoire sur la Sphoeristique, p. 117—153; and first Memoire sur les Ath∣letes,
